been%20a%20dream%20in%20the%20making%20for%20a%20while%2C%26quot%3B%20Jesper%20Brodin%2C%20chief%20executive%20of%20Ingka%2C%20the%20main%20operator%20of%20Ikea%20stores%2C%20told%20FT.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20a%20place%20in%20Ikea%20where%20we%20can%20do%20more%20advanced%20and%20cool%20stuff.%20There%20is%20an%20incredible%20confidence%20in%20the%20company%20evolving%20on%20digital.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESellers%20list%20their%20pre-owned%20Ikea%20products%20on%20the%20marketplace%20with%20their%20own%20photos%20and%20listing%20price%2C%20and%20the%20site's%20AI-enabled%20database%20automatically%20populates%20details%20like%20dimensions%20and%20promotional%20images%20into%20the%20listing%2C%20FT%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BWith%20this%20marketplace%20we%20want%20to%20enable%20people%20to%20connect%20and%20support%20each%20other%20to%20fulfil%20the%20needs%20and%20dreams%20of%20a%20home%20and%20have%20access%20to%20an%20even%20more%20affordable%20IKEA%20range%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Ikea%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20spokesperson%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20global%20second-hand%20furniture%20market%20is%20growing%20rapidly%2C%20with%20a%20projected%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%206.4%25%20in%202024.%20Already%20today%2C%2010%25%20of%20the%20second-hand%20home%20furnishing%20market%20is%20made%20up%20by%20IKEA%20products.%20With%20the%20platform%20that%20we%20are%20testing%20in%20Madrid%20and%20Oslo%2C%20we%20have%20the%20possibilities%20to%20simplify%20and%20enhance%20the%20experience%20for%20both%20the%20seller%20and%20the%20buyer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20listings%20on%20the%20marketplace%20are%20free%2C%20but%20Brodin%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20Ikea%20may%20charge%20a%20%26quot%3Bsymbolic%26quot%3B%20fee%20in%20the%20future.%20Sellers%20listing%20pre-owned%20items%20on%20the%20marketplace%20can%20receive%20cash%20payments%20or%20an%20Ikea%20voucher%20with%20a%2015%25%20bonus%2C%20per%20FT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20verify%20the%20full%20scope%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fikea-employee-turnover-problem-increased-wages-flexibility-retail-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeconomics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Brodin%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20use%20the%20offer%20to%20get%20a%20discount%20with%20Ikea%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20good%20way%20to%20reconnect%20with%20customers.%20I%20am%20very%20curious.%20I%20think%20it%20makes%20business%20sense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fikea-preowned-furniture-secondhand-online-marketplace-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724802889000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cd09cf1aa2ac29ee3477c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fikea-preowned-furniture-secondhand-online-marketplace-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ikea%20launched%20a%20secondhand%20marketplace%20for%20customers%20to%20buy%20pre-owned%20items%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20compete%20with%20resale%20sites%2C%20Financial%20Times%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fikea-preowned-furniture-secondhand-online-marketplace-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zee%2C%20Sony%20settle%20dispute%20over%20aborted%20%2410%20billion%20merger%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724802504000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112850525%2Cimgsize-558924.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fzee-sony-sett