%20despite%20the%20Fed%20being%20set%20to%20cut%20rates%20in%20September.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHiring%20conditions%20have%20been%20weakening%2C%20with%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20spiking%20past%204%25%20in%20July.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Reserve's%20efforts%20to%20boost%20the%20economy%20may%20be%20coming%20too%20late%2C%20according%20to%20Northwestern%20Mutual.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20financial%20services%20firm%20flagged%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20potential%20recession%2C%20even%20as%20the%20Fed%20looks%20poised%20to%20cut%20rates%20to%20keep%20the%20economy%20stimulated.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20are%20pricing%20in%20with%20certainty%20that%20the%20Fed%20will%20begin%20easing%20monetary%20policy%20in%20September%2C%20according%20to%20the%20CME%20FedWatch%20tool%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20may%20not%20prevent%20a%20recession%2C%20given%20the%20weakness%20in%20the%20economy%2C%20according%20to%20Brent%20Schutte%2C%20the%20firm's%20chief%20investment%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20all%20think%20because%20the%20Fed%20is%20cutting%20rates%2C%20that's%20the%20magic%20elixir%20that's%20going%20to%20allow%20us%20to%20avoid%20a%20recession%2C%26quot%3B%20Schutte%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Fvideo%2F2024%2F08%2F27%2Ffed-rate-cuts-may-not-help-economy-avoid-recession-says-northwestern-mutuals-schutte.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20pegging%20the%20probability%20of%20a%20downturn%20at%20over%2050%25.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20past%20four%20recessions%2C%20the%20Fed%20has%20actually%20cut%20before%20the%20recession%20and%20still%20had%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20strategists%20have%20noted%20that%20Fed%20rate%20cuts%20have%20typically%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frate-cuts-recession-economy-labor-market-federal-reserve-bca-research-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epre