tps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdunkin-doughnut-flavors-ranked-worst-to-best-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoughnut%3C%2Fa%3E%20straight%20out%20of%20the%20fryer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20recent%20trip%20to%20Portland%2C%20Maine%2C%20from%20Connecticut%2C%20I%20stopped%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theholydonut.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Holy%20Donut%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20famous%20doughnut%20shop%20that%20has%20been%20featured%20on%20television%20shows%20like%20%26quot%3BMan%20vs.%20Food%26quot%3B%20and%20gained%20a%20reputation%20for%20its%20unique%20potato-doughnut%20recipe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Holy%20Donut%20opened%20its%20doors%20in%202012%20as%20a%20small%20business%20and%20has%20since%20grown%20into%20a%20Maine%20institution%2C%20with%20five%20locations%20across%20the%20state.%20I%20visited%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-donut-shops-us-2018-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoughnut%20shop%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Park%20Avenue%20location%20in%20Portland%2C%20the%20first%20shop%20the%20family-run%20business%20opened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20four%20of%20The%20Holy%20Donut's%20most%20popular%20flavors%20and%20saw%20firsthand%20why%20this%20small%20business%20has%20become%20one%20of%20Portland's%20best%20not-so-hidden%20gems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20visit%20any%20of%20The%20Holy%20Donut's%20locations%2C%20you%20must%20try%20these%20doughnut%20flavors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20arrived%20at%20The%20Holy%20Donut's%20Park%20Avenue%20location%20at%20around%2010%20a.m.%20on%20a%20Sunday.%20The%20place%20was%20already%20heaving.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20holy%20donut%20in%20portland%20maine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8faac1aa2ac29ee33e8e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Holy%20Donut's%20oldest%20location%20is%20located%20on%20Park%20Avenue%20in%20Portland%2C%20Maine.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Holy%20Donut%20was%20dreamed%20up%20by%20single%20mother%20Leigh%20Kellis%20in%20her%20apartment%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20business%20has%20since%20grown%20into%20a%20local%20institution%20with%20five%20locations%20and%20now%20has%20even%20bigger%20dreams%2C%20largely%20thanks%20to%20the%20efforts%20of%20CEO%20and%20co-owner%20Jeff%20Buckwalter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20big%20part%20of%20our%20story%20is%20it's%20a%20wonderful%20American%20dream%20story.%20The%20family%20coming%20together%20and%20just%20figuring%20it%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%20during%20a%20visit%20to%20The%20Holy%20Donut%20in%20August.%20%26quot%3BAlso%2C%20within%20a%20community%20that%20has%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20know%20that%20it%20doesn't%20exist%20outside%20Portland%20%E2%80%94%20but%20has%20a%20rising%20tides%20mentality.%20Everybody%20is%20willing%20to%20help%20everybody.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhen%20I%20walked%20through%20the%20doors%2C%20I%20could%20smell%20the%20sweet%20icing%20and%20dough%20being%20fried.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22donuts%20being%20made%20in%20the%20fryer%20at%20the%20holy%20donut%20in%20portland%20maine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8fab51aa2ac29ee33e8e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Holy%20Donut%20hand-fries%20all%20of%20its%20doughnuts.%20%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBuckwalter%20said%20that%20while%20the%20Park%20Avenue%20location%20is%20pretty%20busy%2C%20the%20busiest%20location%20is%20on%20Commercial%20Street%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20Old%20Port.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20all%20of%20its%20locations%2C%20he%20said%20they%20probably%20sell%20around%20six%20or%20seven%20million%20doughnuts%20each%20year%2C%20mostly%20during%20the%20summer%20at%20the%20height%20of%20tourism%20in%20Maine%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20he%20hopes%20to%20expand%20into%20shipping%20in%20order%20to%20sell%20even%20more%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20going%20to%20own%20the%20doughnut%20shipping%20space%20nationwide%20and%20we%20are%20going%20to%20be%20known%20as%20a%20very%20well-managed%20and%20scaled%20family%20company%20that%20now%20has%20a%20nationwide%20brand%2C%26quot%3B%20Buckwalter%20said%20of%20his%20goals%20for%20The%20Holy%20Donut%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20some%20of%20the%20chain's%20most%20popular%20doughnuts%20to%20see%20what%20all%20the%20fuss%20was%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20first%20flavor%20I%20tried%20was%20the%20dark%20chocolate%20coconut%20doughnut.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dark%20chocolate%20coconut%20donut%20from%20the%20holy%20donut%20in%20portland%20maine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8fa2143b5e59d16b4e46d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20dark%20chocolate%20coconut%20doughnut%20came%20covered%20in%20large%20flakes%20of%20coconut.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20doughnut%20was%20completely%20covered%20in%20large%20coconut%20flakes.%20As%20a%20huge%20fan%20of%20the%20Girl%20Scout%20cookie%20Samoas%2C%20I%20was%20interested%20to%20see%20if%20this%20flavor%20combination%20was%20similar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20first%20things%20I%20noticed%20about%20this%20doughnut%20was%20its%20weight%20and%20size%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20heavier%20than%20doughnuts%20I've%20had%20in%20the%20past%20and%20I%20wondered%20if%20that%20was%20due%20to%20the%20inclusion%20of%20potatoes%20in%20The%20Holy%20Donut's%20recipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bonappetit.com%2Fentertaining-style%2Ftrends-news%2Farticle%2Fpotato-doughnuts-the-holy-donut%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBon%20Appetit%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%202016%20that%20the%20business%20credits%20%26quot%3BThe%20Joy%20of%20Cooking%26quot%3B%20with%20giving%20founder%20Leigh%20Kellis%20the%20original%20idea%20for%20a%20potato%20doughnut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKellis%20also%20discovered%20that%20when%20she%20added%20riced%20potatoes%20to%20the%20recipe%2C%20the%20doughnuts%20came%20out%20fluffier%20and%20didn't%20dry%20out%20as%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20doughnut%20had%20a%20cake-like%20consistency.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dark%20chocolate%20coconut%20donut%20from%20the%20holy%20donut%20in%20portland%20maine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8fa21c72ebc54a40e8e53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20dark%20chocolate%20and%20coconut%20doughnut%20tasted%20a%20lot%20like%20cake.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20coconut%20had%20a%20slightly%20sweet%20flavor%20that%20wasn't%20too%20overpowering%2C%20and%20the%20chocolate%20flavor%20also%20came%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cake%20part%20of%20the%20doughnut%20was%20thick%20without%20being%20too%20stodgy.%20It%20was%20distinctly%20different%20from%20other%20doughnuts%20I've%20tried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20more%20filling%20and%20substantial%2C%20though%20I%20wasn't%20complaining%20about%20that%20considering%20this%20doughnut%20cost%20%245.%20You%20can%20also%20order%20a%20half-dozen%20of%20assorted%20donuts%20for%20%2422%2C%20or%20a%20full%20dozen%20for%20%2444.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20doughnuts%20I%20tried%20were%20given%20to%20me%2C%20free%20of%20charge%2C%20when%20I%20tasted%20them%20during%20my%20behind-the-scenes%20visit%20to%20The%20Holy%20Donut.%20However%2C%20I%20returned%20a%20few%20days%20later%20to%20purchase%20the%20same%20flavors%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0except%20the%20savory%20bacon%20and%20cheddar%20doughnut%2C%20which%20had%20sold%20out%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0so%20I%20could%20try%20them%20again.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20also%20tried%20the%20dark%20chocolate%20and%20sea%20salt%20doughnut.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dark%20chocolate%20sea%20salt%20donut%20from%20the%20holy%20donut%20in%20portland%20maine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8fa211aa2ac29ee33e8a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20dark%20chocolate%20and%20sea%20salt%20doughnut%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20flavors.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBuckwalter%20told%20me%20this%20flavor%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20%E2%80%94%20if%20not%20%3Cem%3Ethe%3C%2Fem%3E%20most%20%E2%80%94%20popular%20doughnuts%20The%20Holy%20Donut%20sells.%20It's%20a%20dark%20chocolate%20and%20sea%20salt%20base%20covered%20in%20a%20simple%20icing%20glaze.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20could%20really%20taste%20the%20sea%20salt%2C%20which%20gave%20this%20doughnut%20a%20dynamic%20flavor%20profile.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dark%20chocolate%20sea%20salt%20donut%20from%20the%20holy%20donut%20in%20portland%20maine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8fa211aa2ac29ee33e8a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20slight%20saltiness%20offset%20the%20sweetness%20of%20the%20chocolate.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20slightly%20salty%20flavor%20balanced%20out%20the%20sweetness%20of%20the%20chocolate%20doughnut%20and%20the%20light%20layer%20of%20glaze.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20doughnut%20was%20also%20slightly%20thinner%20than%20the%20coconut%20doughnut%2C%20which%20made%20it%20a%20touch%20easier%20to%20eat.%20I%20could%20have%20easily%20polished%20off%20one%20or%20even%20two%20of%20these%20doughnuts.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20doughnut%20costs%20%244.25%2C%20excluding%20tax%2C%20and%20is%20also%20available%20in%20a%20gluten-free%20version%20for%20%245.25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20also%20had%20to%20try%20a%20savory%20doughnut.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bacon%20cheddar%20donut%20from%20the%20holy%20donut%20in%20portland%20maine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8fadf43b5e59d16b4e4e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bacon%20cheddar%20doughnut%20had%20an%20impressive%20cheese%20pull.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20watching%20the%20bacon%20cheddar%20doughnuts%20being%20made%20right%20in%20front%20of%20me%2C%20I%20had%20to%20try%20one.%20It%20was%20a%20unique%20menu%20item%20that%20reminded%20me%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20bacon%2C%20egg%2C%20and%20cheese%20sandwich%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20most%20of%20the%20other%20doughnuts%20sold%20by%20The%20Holy%20Donut%2C%20the%20bacon%20cheddar%20doughnut%20doesn't%20have%20a%20hole%20and%20is%20made%20with%20plain%20dough%20stuffed%20with%20bacon%20and%20half-melted%20sharp%20cheddar%20cheese.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20bacon%20was%20smoky%20and%20savory%2C%20and%20the%20cheddar%20cheese%20added%20a%20sharp%20flavor.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bacon%20cheddar%20donut%20from%20the%20holy%20donut%20in%20portland%20maine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8fae81aa2ac29ee33e91d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bacon%20and%20cheddar%20doughnut%20was%20a%20savory%20breakfast%20option.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plain%20doughnut%20encasing%20the%20ingredients%20was%20crispy%20and%20bread-like%2C%20allowing%20the%20flavors%20of%20the%20bacon%20and%20cheese%20to%20shine%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20only%20criticism%20is%20that%20the%20dough%20was%20a%20touch%20dry.%20A%20simple%20pat%20of%20butter%20would%20have%20moistened%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20could%20also%20have%20been%20an%20effect%20of%20the%20dough%20used%20to%20make%20these%20doughnuts%2C%20which%20were%20%26quot%3Bsecond%20cuts%26quot%3B%20or%20put-back-together%20dough%20after%20previous%20doughnuts%20had%20been%20rolled%20out%20and%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20second%20cuts%2C%20they%20behave%20a%20little%20differently%2C%26quot%3B%20Buckwalter%20said%2C%20adding%20they%20have%20a%20little%20more%20gluten%20than%20other%20doughnuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20doughnut%20I%20was%20most%20excited%20to%20try%20after%20seeing%20it%20being%20made%20was%20the%20seasonal%20blueberry%20doughnut.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22donuts%20being%20made%20at%20the%20holy%20donut%20in%20portland%20maine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8facd1aa2ac29ee33e8f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20watched%20an%20employee%20hand-glaze%20each%20of%20the%20blueberry%20donuts.%20%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20smell%20of%20the%20blueberry%20glaze%20wafted%20throughout%20the%20doughnut%20shop%20throughout%20the%20morning%20I%20visited%2C%20which%20fell%20right%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20Maine's%20blueberry%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Holy%20Donut%20was%20offering%20four%20different%20seasonal%20blueberry%20flavors%20through%20Labor%20Day%3A%20blueberry%20glazed%2C%20blueberry%20lemon%2C%20blueberry%20cinnamon%20sugar%2C%20and%20holy%20cannoli%20blueberry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBoth%20the%20dough%20used%20t