oin%20has%20rallied%20soaring%2045%25%20this%20year%20amid%20the%20excitement%20over%20new%20bitcoin%20ETFs.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20rally%20has%20also%20come%20as%20more%20mainstream%20investors%20enter%20the%20space.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20crypto%20rallies%2C%20the%20number%20of%20bitcoin%20millionaires%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20in%20the%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20new%20report%20from%20New%20World%20Wealth%20and%20Henley%20%26amp%3B%20Partners%2C%20the%20number%20of%20bitcoin%20millionaires%20has%20risen%20to%2085%2C400%2C%20a%20111%25%20increase%20in%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20number%20of%20crypto%20millionaires%20in%20general%20soared%20to%20172%2C300%2C%20up%20from%20just%2088%2C200%20last%20year%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rapid%20increase%20in%20crypto%20millionaires%20comes%20as%20newly%20approved%20spot%20ETFs%20in%20the%20US%20have%20pushed%20bitcoin%20to%20new%20highs%20in%202024.%20It%20his%20an%20all-time%20high%20above%20%2473%2C000%20in%20March.%20It%20has%20since%20pared%20that%20gain%20but%20is%20still%20up%20by%20about%2045%25%20to%20around%20%2464%2C000.%20The%20price%20of%20bitcoin%20us%20up%20138%25%20in%20the%20last%2012%20months.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20bitcoin%20ETFs%20have%20garnered%20over%20%2450%20billion%20in%20assets%20since%20hitting%20the%20market%20in%20January%20after%20a%20yearslong%20struggle%20to%20get%20the%20funds%20approved%20by%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cryptocurrency%20landscape%20of%202024%20bears%20little%20resemblance%20to%20its%20predecessors%2C%26quot%3B%20Dominic%20Volek%2C%20Henley%20%26amp%3B%20Partners'%20head%20of%20private%20clients%2C%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBitcoin's%20rise%20to%20over%20USD%2073%2C000%20in%20March%20set%20a%20new%20all-time%20high%2C%20while%20the%20long-awaited%20approval%20of%20spot%20Bitcoin%20and%20Ethereum%20ETFs%20in%20the%20USA%20unleashed%20a%20torrent%20of%20institutional%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrypto's%20total%20market%20value%20is%20now%20at%20%242.3%20trillion%2C%20up%2089%25%20from%20its%20%241.2%20trillion%20valuation%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVolek%20added%20that%20as%20investors%20are%20now%20preparing%20for%20potential%20Solana%20ETFs%2C%20the%20series%20of%20industry%20milestones%20has%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20broader%20crypto%20adoption%2C%20%26quot%3Bone%20where%20digital%20assets%20increasingly%20cross-pollinate%20with%20traditional%20finance%20and%20global%20mobility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20finding%20extraordinary%20success%20in%20the%20industry%20in%20the%20last%20year%20are%20six%20new%20crypto%20billionaires%2C%20making%20for%2028%20crypto%20billionaires%20worldwide.%20The%20report%20says%20most%20of%20those%20new%20crypto%20billionaires%20owe%20their%20success%20to%20bitcoin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20the%20six%20new%20crypto%20billionaires%20created%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20five%20came%20from%20Bitcoin%2C%20underscoring%20its%20dominant%20position%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20attracting%20long-term%20investors%20who%20buy%20large%20holdings%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrew%20Amoils%2C%20New%20World%20Wealth's%20head%20of%20research%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20of%20the%20report%20say%20that%20with%20so%20many%20new%20crypto%20millionaires%20and%20billionaires%2C%20there's%20more%20focus%20on%20which%20countries%20have%20the%20most%20crypto-friendly%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHenley%20%26amp%3B%20Partners%20has%20seen%20a%20significant%20uptick%20in%20crypto-wealthy%20clients%20seeking%20alternative%20residence%20and%20citizenship%20options%20in%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESingapore%20and%20Hong%20Kong%20are%20particularly%20attractive%20options%20for%20their%20tax%20policies%20and%20regulatory%20frameworks%20relating%20to%20crypto%2C