tion%3EThe%20Gothic%20Room.%3Cp%3EGavin%20Ashworth%20%E2%80%94%20The%20Preservation%20Society%20of%20Newport%20County%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ribbed%20ceiling%2C%20stone%20mantlepiece%2C%20and%20wood%20floors%20were%20all%20imported%20from%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAlva%20Vanderbilt%20purchased%20the%20art%20collection%20%26quot%3Ben%20bloc%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20all%20together%20in%20a%20set.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stained-glass%20windows%20in%20the%20Gothic%20Room%20at%20Marble%20House.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccb40e43b5e59d16b52bba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStained-glass%20windows%20in%20the%20Gothic%20Room.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20art%20collections%20%26quot%3Ben%20bloc%26quot%3B%20was%20popular%20during%20the%20Gilded%20Age%20as%20a%20way%20to%20quickly%20acquire%20a%20status%20symbol%20instead%20of%20taking%20generations%20to%20build%20a%20collection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Morning%20Room%20also%20functioned%20as%20a%20library.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Morning%20Room%20at%20Marble%20House.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccb40ec72ebc54a40ed60b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Morning%20Room.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wooden%20bookcases%2C%20built%20in%20Paris%20by%20Allard%20and%20Sons%2C%20held%20books%20on%20architecture%20and%20European%20history%20that%20were%20original%20to%20the%20Vanderbilt%20family's%20collection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Grand%20Salon%20was%20also%20called%20the%20Gold%20Room%20because%20of%20the%2022-karat%20gold%20leaf%20covering%20every%20wall.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221197%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Salon%2C%20or%20Gold%20Room%2C%20at%20Marble%20House.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cc9e671aa2ac29ee341b28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Grand%20Salon.%3Cp%3EThe%20Preservation%20Society%20of%20Newport%20County%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20room%20is%20really%20the%20epitome%20of%20the%20Gilded%20Age%2C%26quot%3B%20Caitlin%20Emery%2C%20the%20research%20and%20interpretation%20coordinator%20at%20the%20Preservation%20Society%20of%20Newport%20County%2C%20said%20on%20the%20audio%20tour.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20coated%20in%20gold%20and%20you%20have%20to%20imagine%20guests%20coming%20in%20on%20a%20summer%20evening%20with%20the%20sun%20going%20down.%20And%20the%20light%20picking%20up%20on%20all%20these%20gilded%20surfaces.%20The%20feel%20and%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20room%20would%20have%20been%20absolutely%20remarkable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Vanderbilts%20used%20it%20as%20a%20ballroom.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Grand%20Salon%20at%20Marble%20House.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccb85bc72ebc54a40edad4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Grand%20Salon.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201895%2C%20the%20Vanderbilts%20hosted%20a%20ball%20to%20celebrate%20their%20daughter%20Consuelo%20Vanderbilt's%20engagement%20to%20Charles%20Spencer-Churchhill%2C%20the%20ninth%20Duke%20of%20Marlborough.%20The%20party%20featured%20300%20guests%20and%20lasted%20until%205%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsuelo%20Vanderbilt%20was%20secretly%20engaged%20to%20another%20man%20and%20resisted%20the%20arrangement%2C%20but%20she%20wrote%20that%20her%20mother%20%26quot%3Bwould%20not%20hesitate%20to%20shoot%26quot%3B%20her%20lover%20if%20she%20tried%20to%20run%20away%20with%20him.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlva%20wanted%20to%20secure%20for%20her%20daughter%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20money%20couldn't%20buy%20%E2%80%94%20a%20title%2C%26quot%3B%20Emery%20said%20in%20the%20audio%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheirs%20was%20a%20loveless%20marriage.%20After%2026%20years%2C%20Alva%20Vanderbilt%20testified%20that%20she%20had%20forced%20her%20daughter%20to%20marry%20the%20duke%2C%20which%20allowed%20her%20to%20receive%20an%20annulment%20in%201921.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20tour%20continued%20up%20the%20grand%20staircase%20on%20the%20second%20floor.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20second%20floor%20of%20Marble%20House.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccc17e1aa2ac29ee344f7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20second%20floor.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mezzanine%20level%20featured%20two%20private%20studies%2C%20one%20for%20William%20K.%20Vanderbilt%20and%20one%20for%20Alva%20Vanderbilt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EConsuelo%20Vanderbilt's%20bedroom%20appeared%20as%20George%20Russell's%20room%20on%20the%20HBO%20show%20%26quot%3BThe%20Gilded%20Age.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Consuelo%20Vanderbilt's%20bedroom%20at%20Marble%20House.%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccb85b43b5e59d16b53010%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EConsuelo%20Vanderbilt's%20bedroom.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EConsuelo%20Vanderbilt%20moved%20to%20Marble%20House%20when%20she%20was%2015.%20She%20described%20her%20room%20as%20%26quot%3Baustere%2C%26quot%3B%20writing%20that%20her%20mother%20had%20picked%20out%20every%20piece%20of%20furniture%20and%20%26quot%3Bforbidden