ious%20role%20on%20December%201%2C%202024.%20Shah%20was%20the%20sole%20nominee%20for%20the%20chairmanship%20after%20current%20Chair%20Barclay%20decided%20not%20to%20seek%20a%20third%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20his%20election%2C%20Shah%20expressed%20his%20intent%20to%20advance%20the%20global%20reach%20and%20popularity%20of%20cricket%2C%20particularly%20with%20its%20upcoming%20inclusion%20in%20the%20Los%20Angeles%202028%20Olympics%E2%80%94a%20moment%20he%20views%20as%20a%20pivotal%20opportunity%20for%20the%20sport's%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20humbled%20by%20the%20nomination%20as%20the%20Chair%20of%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20stated%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20committed%20to%20working%20closely%20with%20the%20ICC%20team%20and%20our%20member%20nations%20to%20further%20globalize%20cricket.%20We%20stand%20at%20a%20critical%20juncture%20where%20it%20is%20increasingly%20important%20to%20balance%20the%20coexistence%20of%20multiple%20formats%2C%20promote%20the%20adoption%20of%20advanced%20technologies%2C%20and%20introduce%20our%20marquee%20events%20to%20new%20global%20markets.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20cricket%20more%20inclusive%20and%20popular%20than%20ever%20before.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%2C%20who%20will%20be%20turning%2036%20next%20month%2C%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20will%20build%20on%20the%20valuable%20lessons%20learned%2C%20we%20must%20also%20embrace%20fresh%20thinking%20and%20innovation%20to%20elevate%20the%20love%20for%20cricket%20worldwide.%20The%20inclusion%20of%20our%20sport%20in%20the%20Olympics%20at%20LA%202028%20represents%20a%20significant%20inflexion%20point%20for%20the%20growth%20of%20cricket%2C%20and%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20it%20will%20drive%20the%20sport%20forward%20in%20unprecedented%20ways.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah's%20election%20marks%20a%20new%20chapter%20for%20the%20ICC%20as%20it%20seeks%20to%20expand%20the%20game's%20reach%20and%20continue%20its%20evolution%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20He%20is%20the%20fifth%20Indian%20to%20hold%20a%20prominent%20post%20at%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EN.%20Srinivasan%20(2014-15)%20and%20Shashank%20Manohar%20(2016-2020)%20have%20held%20the%20post%20of%20Chairman%20of%20the%20ICC%20while%20Jagmohan%20Dalmiya%20(1997%20to%202000)%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20(2010-2012)%20are%20two%20Indians%20who%20have%20held%20the%20position%20of%20President%20of%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724770980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fnrfj9sp_jay-shah-bcci_625x300_24_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Folympics-at-la-2028-jay-shahs-big-announcement-right-after-becoming-icc-chairman-6430760%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20Delhi%2C%20Aug%2027%20(IANS)%20India's%20Jay%20Shah%20was%20on%20Tuesday%20elected%20unopposed%20as%20the%20next%20Independent%20Chair%20of%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20and%20will%20be%20taking%20over%20from%20Greg%20Barclay%20in%20December%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Folympics-at-la-2028-jay-shahs-big-announcement-right-after-becoming-icc-chairman-6430760%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tim%20Walz%20posed%20with%20two%20different%20dogs%20but%20Republicans%20think%20he's%20lying%3A%20Viral%20post%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724770972000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112843375%2Cimgsize-1055275.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2F