3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsamsung-launches-ai-powered-washing-machine-aims-to-lead-premium-segment-124082701008_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNeed%20To%20Teach%20Boys%20To%20Respect%20Women%26quot%3B%3A%20High%20Court%20On%20Sex%20Assault%20Cases%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20mindset%20of%20boys%20needs%20to%20be%20changed%20and%20they%20need%20to%20be%20taught%20to%20respect%20women%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20advised%20today%20while%20hearing%20a%20petition%20on%20the%20case%20of%20sexual%20assault%20on%20two%20four-year-olds%20inside%20their%20school%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Badlapur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20change%20the%20mindset%20of%20the%20boys%20when%20they%20are%20young.%20Teach%20them%20to%20respect%20the%20other%20gender%2C%20respect%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Revati%20Mohite%20Dere%20and%20Prithiviraj%20Chavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20that%20was%20hearing%20the%20case%20taken%20up%20suo%20moto%20(on%20its%20own)%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bmale%20chauvinism%26quot%3B%20persists%20in%20our%20society%20and%20that%20nothing%20will%20change%20until%20children%20are%20taught%20about%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMale%20dominance%20and%20male%20chauvinism%20are%20still%20there.%20Until%20we%20teach%20our%20children%20at%20home%20about%20equality%2C%20nothing%20will%20happen.%20Till%20then%2C%20all%20these%20laws%20like%20Nirbhaya%20and%20all%20will%20not%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20always%20speak%20about%20girls.%20Why%20don't%20we%20tell%20boys%20what%20is%20right%20and%20wrong%3F%20We%20need%20to%20change%20the%20mindset%20of%20boys%20when%20they%20are%20young.%20Teach%20them%20to%20respect%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20kindergarten%20students%20were%20allegedly%20sexually%20abused%20by%20a%20school%20attendant.%20The%20incident%20triggered%20huge%20protests%20with%20the%20state%20government%20assuring%20strict%20action%20against%20the%20culprit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20suggested%20forming%20a%20committee%20comprising%20a%20retired%20policeman%2C%20retired%20judge%2C%20retired%20educator%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee%20(CWC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20a%20consolidated%20committee%20which%20can%20come%20up%20with%20recommendations%20on%20how%20these%20acts%20can%20be%20curbed%20in%20schools%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20High%20Court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20can%20come%20up%20with%20recommendations%20on%20how%20these%20incidents%20can%20be%20curbed%20in%20schools%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20also%20sought%20to%20know%20if%20the%20school%20ran%20a%20background%20check%20on%20the%20accused%20before%20hiring%20him%20and%20why%20the%20students%20were%20sent%20will%20a%20male%20attendant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Advocate%20General%20(AG)%20said%20the%20background%20check%20wasn't%20done.%20The%20accused's%20parents%20and%20cousins%20work%20in%20the%20same%20school%20and%20since%20he%20was%20also%20hired%2C%20said%20the%20AG.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20slammed%20the%20lapses%20by%20the%20police%20in%20the%20case.%20%26quot%3BThe%20mandate%20of%20the%20law%20is%20not%20followed%20by%20Badlapur%20police.%20They%20attempted%20to%20record%20the%20victim%20girl's%20statements%20at%20the%20police%20station.%20There%20is%20complete%20non-compliance%20with%20the%20mandate.%20Asking%20the%20victim%20and%20her%20parents%20to%20come%20to%20the%20police%20station%20for%20a%20statement%20recording%20is%20completely%20insensitive%20and%20against%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20also%20suggested%20that%20a%20woman%20doctor%20must%20examine%20minor%20survivors%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20while%20expressing%20displeasure%20that%20a%20male%20doctor%20had%20initially%20examined%20the%20nursery%20school%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20that%20a%20woman%20prosecutor%20should%20be%20appointed%20to%20assist%20the%20special%20prosecutor%20in%20the%20case%20She%20should%20be%20there%20with%20the%20girls%20and%20help%20them%2C%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724767980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2F85mh9qus_bombay-high-court-website-photo_625x300_20_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbadlapur-sexual-assault-case-bombay-high-court-on-sex-assault-cases-need-to-teach-boys-to-respect-women-6430395%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20mindset%20of%20boys%20needs%20to%20be%20changed%20and%20they%20need%20to%20be%20taught%20to%20respect%20women%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20advised%20today%20while%20hearing%20a%20petition%20on%20the%20case%20of%20sexual%20assault%20on%20two%20four-year-olds%20inside%20their%20school%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Badlapur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbadlapur-sexual-assault-case-bombay-high-court-on-sex-assault-cases-need-to-teach-boys-to-respect-women-6430395%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Pension%20Row%2C%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman's%20Sharp%20Counter%20To%20Congress'%20%26quot%3BU-Turn%26quot%3B%20Jab%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFinance%20Minister%20on%20Tuesday%20joined%20the%20government's%20pushback%20against%20the%20Congress's%20%26quot%3Bgovernment%20of%20U-turns%26quot%3B%20jibe%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Funified-pension-scheme%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnified%20Pension%20Scheme%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20UPS%2C%20proposal.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20a%20government%20of%20U-turns...%20we%20give%20flexible%2C%20choice-driven%20governance%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20shot%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Finance%20Minister%20criticised%20the%20Congress%20for%20failing%20to%20understand%20the%20UPS%20is%20not%20a%20rollback%20to%20the%20pre-2004%20pension%20plan%2C%20and%20that%20it%20will%20improve%20the%20current%20National%20Pension%20System%2C%20or%20NPS.%20She%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20non-BJP%20ruled%20states%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20UPS%20will%20be%20implemented%20sooner%20or%20later...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20ministry%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20the%20government%20would%20not%20%26quot%3Bmarket%26quot%3B%20the%20new%20pension%20scheme%20to%20states%20unwilling%20to%20adopt%20it%3B%20there%20is%20no%20compulsion%20to%20do%20so%2C%20sources%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20also%20said%20the%20'architecture'%20of%20the%20new%20pension%20scheme%20has%20been%20given%20to%20all%20states%2C%20whether%20ruled%20by%20the%20BJP%20or%20an%20opposition%20party%2C%20and%20it%20is%20for%20each%20to%20weigh%20pros%20and%20cons%20and%20decide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%202022%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20election%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20Congress%20said%20it%20would%20implement%20the%20old%20scheme%20if%20it%20won%20power.%20The%20party%20secured%20a%20strong%20win%2C%20claiming%2040%20of%20its%2068%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20further%20said%20the%20new%20pension%20scheme%20is%20not%20applicable%20to%20public%20sector%20or%20employees%20of%20central%20or%20state-run%20banks%2C%20or%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%20who%20will%20continue%20with%20the%20older%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20major%20announcement%20ahead%20of%20elections%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Haryana%20in%20September-October%2C%20as%20well%20as%20those%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20Jharkhand%20later%20this%20year%2C%20the%20government%20launched%20the%20Unified%20Pension%20Scheme%20-%20to%20be%20implemented%20from%20April%201%20next%20year%20-%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca