-reups-rigged-election-charge-on-back-of-mark-zuckerbergs-admission%2Famp_articleshow%2F112841766.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Judge%20orders%20'Pharma%20Bro'%20Shkreli%20to%20return%20rare%20Wu-Tang%20album%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724765869000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Ff8d6%2Flive%2F4d473270-6469-11ef-b970-9f202720b57a.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp8nz000j81o%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Martin%20Shkreli%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp8nz000j81o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp8nz000j81o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp8nz000j81o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Students%20Protest%20Against%20Canadian%20Government%20Over%20Deportation%20Fears%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20Indian%20student%20graduates%20have%20staged%20protests%20against%20a%20new%20federal%20policy%20in%20Canada%20that%20puts%20them%20at%20risk%20of%20getting%20deported%20from%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20international%20students%2C%20particularly%20those%20from%20India%2C%20dream%20of%20moving%20to%20the%20North%20American%20country%20in%20hopes%20of%20building%20a%20better%20life%2C%20but%20the%20announced%20immigration%20policies%20changes%20have%20left%20the%20future%20of%20more%20than%2070%2C000%20student%20graduates%20in%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20students%20have%20camped%20in%20front%20of%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20in%20Canada's%20Prince%20Edward%20Island%20province%2C%20protesting%20the%20sudden%20policy%20change%20for%20more%20than%20three%20months.%20Similar%20demonstrations%20were%20also%20seen%20in%20the%20provinces%20of%20Ontario%2C%20Manitoba%20and%20British%20Columbia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20policies%20are%20aimed%20at%20reducing%20the%20number%20of%20permanent%20residency%20nominations%20by%2025%20per%20cent%20as%20well%20as%20limiting%20study%20permits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20from%20student%20advocacy%20group%20Naujawan%20Support%20Network%20warned%20the%20graduates%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20deported%20when%20their%20work%20permits%20expire%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20spent%20the%20most%20crucial%20six%20years%20of%20my%20life%20taking%20many%20risks%20to%20come%20to%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mehakdeep%20Singh%2C%20a%20former%20international%20student%20who%20is%20facing%20deportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20past%20six%20years%2C%20I%20studied%2C%20I%20worked%2C%20I%20paid%20taxes%2C%20I%20earned%20enough%20CRS%20(Comprehensive%20Ranking%20System)%20points%20but%20the%20government%20has%20just%20taken%20advantage%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20international%20students%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20had%20spent%20his%20family's%20life%20savings%20on%20college%20tuition%20fees%20in%20the%20hopes%20of%20eventually%20gaining%20permanent%20residency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20a%20local%20housing%20and%20jobs%20crisis%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20government%20is%20under%20pressure%20to%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20temporary%20residents%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20a%20staggering%20growth%20in%20recent%20years.%20Mr%20Trudeau%20has%20been%20trailing%20in%20polls%20ahead%20of%20an%20election%20expected%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20government%20is%20also%20reducing%20the%20number%20of%20temporary%20foreign%20workers%20it%20brings%20in%2C%20reversing%20its%20decision%20to%20expand%20the%20programme%20in%202022.%20The%20programme%20allows%20immigrants%20to%20work%20in%20the%20country%20on%20a%20short-term%20basis%2C%20meant%20to%20fill%20labour%20shortages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20looking%20at%20the%20various%20streams%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20as%20we%20move%20forward%2C%20Canada%20remains%20a%20place%20that%20is%20positive%20in%20its%20support%20for%20immigration%2C%20but%20also%20responsible%20in%20the%20way%20we%20integrate%20and%20make%20sure%20there's%20pathways%20to%20success%20for%20everyone%20who%20comes%20to%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20Justin%20Trudeau%20told%20reporters%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20also%20promised%20more%20measures%20to%20reduce%20the%20temporary%20resident%20population%20to%205%25%20of%20Canada's%20total%20population%20in%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Sikh%20Student%20Organization%2C%20an%20advocacy%20group%2C%20insisted%20that%20the%20prevailing%20employment%20and%20housing%20issues%20are%20rooted%20in%20broader%20policy%20failures%20rather%20than%20the%20migration%20of%20international%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724765100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fv5j9jblg_canada-students_625x300_27_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findian-students-in-canada-face-deportation-after-policy-change-6429289%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hundreds%20of%20Indian%20student%20graduates%20have%20staged%20protests%20against%20a%20new%20federal%20policy%20in%20Canada%20that%20puts%20them%20at%20risk%20of%20getting%20deported%20from%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findian-students-in-canada-face-deportation-after-policy-change-6429289%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Actor%20Darshan%20To%20Be%20Shifted%20After%20Row%20Over%20VIP%20Treatment%20In%20Bengaluru%20Jail%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKannada%20actor%20Darshan%20Thoogudeepa%2C%20who%20is%20in%20judicial%20custody%20in%20a%20murder%20case%20is%20being%20shifted%20to