om%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcyvpgd6rlqyo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'144%20Kmph%20To%20128%20Kmph'%3A%20Ex-Pakistan%20Captain%20Namedrops%20Bumrah%20In%20Brutal%20Rant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Pakistan%20captain%20Rashid%20Latif%20has%20rued%20the%20downfall%20of%20the%20side's%20fast-bowling%20stocks%2C%20saying%20the%20pacers%20who%20started%20at%20145kmph%20have%20now%20come%20down%20to%20130%20kmph.%20The%20comments%20from%20Latif%20come%20a%20day%20after%20Pakistan%20lost%20the%20first%20Test%20to%20Bangladesh%20by%20ten%20wickets%2C%20the%20first%20time%20they%20have%20lost%20a%20longer%20format%20game%20at%20home%20by%20this%20margin.%20The%20hosts%20didn't%20field%20a%20frontline%20spinner%20and%20went%20with%20an%20all%20pace-bowling%20attack.%20But%20they%20failed%20to%20contain%20Bangladesh%20on%20a%20docile%20pitch%20as%20the%20visitors'%20made%20565%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20Pakistan%20declaring%20at%20448%2F6.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20day%20five%2C%20Mehidy%20Hasan%20Miraz%20and%20Shakib%20Al%20Hasan%20took%20seven%20wickets%20between%20themselves%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20to%20dismiss%20Pakistan%20for%20just%20146%2C%20and%20Bangladesh%20chased%20down%2030%20in%206.3%20overs%20to%20get%20their%20first-ever%20Test%20win%20over%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20days%20when%20defeats%20against%20a%20team%20like%20Bangladesh%20would%20rankle%2C%20and%20shock%20us.%20We%20were%20a%20formidable%20team%20and%20it%20was%20not%20easy%20to%20beat%20us.%20In%202003%2C%20they%20came%20close%20to%20beating%20us%20thrice%20in%20three%20Tests.%20We%20ended%20up%20winning%20the%20series%203-0.%20The%20aura%20of%20invincibility%20at%20home%20is%20gone.%20We%20have%20lost%20five%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20games%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20knows%20that%20pace%20used%20to%20be%20our%20strength%20but%20our%20top%20fast%20bowlers%20no%20longer%20bowl%20at%20breakneck%20pace.%20It%20was%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20the%20defeat%20yesterday%20(at%20Rawalpindi%20on%20Sunday).%20Their%20speeds%20have%20come%20down%20drastically.%20If%20they%20are%20carrying%20injuries%2C%20they%20should%20reveal%20that.%20Shaheen%20(Afridi)%2C%20Naseem%20(Shah)%2C%20and%20Khurram%20(Shahzad)%20started%20off%20with%20pace%20of%20145.%20They%20all%20have%20come%20down%20to%20130%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Latif%20to%20Cricbuzz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20feels%20the%20Pakistan%20support%20staff%20is%20not%20doing%20a%20good%20job%20of%20keeping%20the%20pacers%20in%20prime%20shape%20to%20hit%20high%20speeds%20in%20Test%20cricket.%20%26quot%3BOur%20trainers%20and%20physios%20are%20to%20blame.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20a%20Jofra%20Archer%2C%20he%20comes%20back%20after%20two%20years%20of%20hiatus%20but%20does%20not%20lose%20a%20yard%20in%20his%20pace.%20Same%20with%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20--%20he%20comes%20back%20from%20an%20operation%20and%20bowls%20with%20the%20same%20velocity.%20Pat%20Cummins...%20he%20was%20out%20of%20cricket%20for%20a%20long%20time%20due%20to%20injury.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20he%20came%20back%2C%20he%20did%20not%20show%20any%20signs%20of%20slowing%20down.%20Why%20are%20our%20bowlers%20slowing%20down%3F%20Obviously%2C%20our%20support%20staff%20is%20not%20doing%20a%20proper%20job.%20A%20bowler%20of%20144%20kmph%20speed%20has%20come%20down%20to%20128%20kmph%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatif%2C%20who%20briefly%20coached%20Afghanistan%2C%20further%20pointed%20out%20how%20Bangladesh%20benefitted%20from%20playing%20spinners%20at%20Rawalpindi%20and%20slammed%20Pakistan%20for%20declaring%20too%20early%20in%20their%20first%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20five-day%20matches%20are%20different%20from%20the%20ODIs%20and%20the%20T20Is.%20Every%20session%20is%20different%20in%20a%20Test.%20Bangladesh%20adapted%20well.%20We%20no%20longer%20have%20quality%20spinners%20like%20we%20used%20to%2C%20so%20turning%20tracks%20are%20no%20longer%20an%20option.%20Instead%2C%20we%20relied%20on%20pace%2C%20but%20the%20tactics%20backfired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20bowlers%20bowled%20too%20short%2C%20while%20Bangladesh%20focused%20on%20fuller%20deliveries%2C%20and%20that%20made%20all%20the%20difference.%20They%20also%20have%20quality%20spinners%20in%20Mehidy%20Hasan%20Miraz%20and%20Shakib%20Al%20Hasan.%20Personally%2C%20I%20would%20have%20also%20included%20Taijul%20Islam%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Latif.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20made%20the%20right%20decision%20by%20opting%20to%20bowl%20first%2C%20given%20the%20conditions%2C%20and%20their%20early%20success%20proved%20it%20was%20the%20correct%20call.%20There%20was%20no%20need%20to%20declare%20(at%20448%20for%20six)%20-%20they%20should%20have%20aimed%20for%20550.%20Falling%20100%20runs%20short%20ultimately%20made%20the%20difference.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(Mohammad)%20Rizwan%20was%20unbeaten%20on%20171%2C%20and%20Shaheen%20was%20also%20batting%20well%20on%2030%20(29).%20Those%20100%20extra%20runs%20cost%20us%20the%20game.%20Bangladesh%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20read%20the%20conditions%20well%20and%20outplayed%20Pakistan.%20They%20wore%20down%20the%20Pakistani%20bowlers%20and%20then%20capitalized%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724763780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F453ndaoo_pakistan-cricket-team-afp_625x300_25_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2F144-kmph-to-128-kmph-ex-pakistan-captain-namedrops-jasprit-bumrah-in-brutal-rant-6420571%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20on%20Sunday%20lost%20the%20first%20Test%20to%20Bangladesh%20by%20ten%20wickets%2C%20the%20first%20time%20they%20have%20lost%20a%20longer%20format%20game%20at%20home%