ain%2C%20anonymous%20insiders%20are%20pulling%20the%20curtain%20on%20the%20dark%20corners%20of%20India's%20startup%20scene%2C%20where%20the%20pressure%20to%20succeed%20justifies%20all%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20claims%20a%20founder%20is%20artificially%20inflating%20revenue%20numbers%20and%20ruthlessly%20slashing%20jobs.%20Another%20accuses%20a%20unicorn%20founder%20of%20backing%20corrupt%20startups%20created%20by%20his%20ex-employees.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhile%20I'm%20still%20bewildered%20by%20these%20accusations%2C%20their%20specificity%20suggests%20they're%20not%20just%20baseless%20rants%2C%20but%20potentially%20true%20claims%20from%20insiders.%20These%20are%20supported%20by%20regulatory%20filings%2C%20public%20and%20private%20conversations%2C%20screenshots%2C%20etc.%20There%20are%20audio%20recordings%2C%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Second%20Coming%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20Twitter%20(now%20X)%20was%20the%20battleground%20where%20handles%20like%20'Unicon%20Baba'%20and%20'Corporate%20Kumar'%20dropped%20bombshells%20about%20the%20dark%20underbelly%20of%20India's%20startup%20scene.%20They%20gave%20us%20an%20unfiltered%20peek%20into%20the%20chaos%20behind%20the%20curtains%20-%20financial%20missteps%2C%20harassment%2C%20and%20the%20kind%20of%20corporate%20governance%20that%20would%20make%20any%20investor%20squirm.%20Despite%20their%20trolling%20and%20the%20toxicity%20they%20brought%20along%2C%20these%20whistleblowers%20highlighted%20genuine%20concerns%20that%2C%20sometimes%2C%20were%20alarmingly%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20suddenly%2C%20around%20the%20time%20COVID%20hit%2C%20most%20of%20these%20Twitter%20(now%20X)%20whistleblower%20accounts%20vanished.%20I%20still%20vividly%20remember%20how%20some%20of%20the%20revelations%20about%20BharatPe%20founder%20Ashneer%20Grover%20created%20a%20storm%20in%20the%20ecosystem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20we%20enter%20another%20funding%20freeze%20and%20navigate%20the%20uncertainties%20of%20AI%2C%20these%20new%20accounts%20offer%20a%20grim%20look%20at%20how%20some%20founders%20are%20playing%20fast%20and%20loose%2C%20not%20just%20with%20finances%20but%20with%20human%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20heavily%20funded%20startups%2C%20there's%20a%20%26quot%3Bvalley%20of%20death%26quot%3B%20ahead.%20Their%20paths%20to%20profitability%20are%20now%20a%20wishful%20dream%2C%20and%20the%20monthly%20cash%20burns%20are%20reducing%20their%20chances%20of%20survival.%20Some%20founders%20are%20resorting%20to%20questionable%20tactics%2C%20including%20mass%20layoffs%2C%20siphoning%20off%20funds%2C%20and%20finding%20an%20escape%20for%20themselves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Lot%20Is%20At%20Stake%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20employees%20are%20taking%20the%20reins%20into%20their%20own%20hands%2C%20bypassing%20manipulated%20Glassdoor%20reviews%20to%20share%20real%20stories%20of%20fraud%20and%20governance%20failures.%20But%20it's%20not%20just%20their%20companies%20that%20pay%20the%20price%20-%20these%20claims%20send%20shockwaves%20through%20the%20entire%20ecosystem.%20Investors%20start%20pulling%20back%2C%20spooked%20by%20one%20bad%20apple%20and%20worried%20about%20the%20whole%20barrel.%20This%20means%20less%20money%20for%20all%20startups%2C%20not%20just%20the%20ones%20caught%20in%20the%20act%2C%20which%20can%20choke%20off%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20scandals%20can%20also%20damage%20India's%20reputation%20as%20a%20startup%20hub.%20And%20it's%20not%20just%20about%20money%20and%20reputation.%20When%20startups%20cut%20corners%2C%20jobs%20are%20on%20the%20line.%20Talented%20folks%20might%20think%20twice%20about%20joining%20a%20startup%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20brain%20drain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20this%20resurgence%20of%20whistleblowers%20important%3F%20Because%20startups%20have%20become%20adept%20at%20gaming%20systems%2C%20be%20it%20investor%20perceptions%20or%20employee%20reviews.%20However%2C%20as%20financial%20pressures%20mount%2C%20the%20veneer%20cracks%20and%20those%20inside%20the%20system%20are%20often%20the%20first%20to%20call%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20sift%20through%20these%20allegations%20and%20stories%2C%20it's%20crucial%20to%20remember%20these%20whistleblowers'%20role%20in%20shaping%20India's%20startup%20ecosystem.%20They%20are%20the%20necessary%20disruptors%20we%20need%20in%20order%20to%20face%20the%20uncomfortable%20truths%20about%20the%20startup%20darlings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20return%20of%20whistleblowers%20is%20a%20healthy%20cleanse%20for%20an%20ecosystem%20fraught%20with%20unchecked%20ambitions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWelcome%20back%2C%20whistleblowers.%20Let's%20keep%20the%20truth%20coming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Pankaj%20Mishra%20has%20been%20a%20journalist%20for%20over%20two%20decades%20and%20is%20the%20co-founder%20of%20FactorDaily.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724760660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F5ail50u_startups_625x300_27_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findias-startup-scene-is-spooked-thanks-to-whistleblowers-6429398%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Once%20again%2C%20anonymous%20insiders%20are%20pulling%20the%20curtain%20on%20the%20dark%20corners%20of%20India's%20startup%20scene%2C%20where%20the%20pressure%20to%20succeed%20justifies%20all%20means.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findias-startup-scene-is-spooked-thanks-to-whistleblowers-6429398%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Won't%20Allow%20Muslims%20To%20Take%20Over%20State%3A%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAssam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20has%20said%20that%20he%20woul%20not%20let%20Bengali-speaking%20Muslims%20take%20over%20the%20state%2C%20underscoring%20that%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20in%20the%20competition%20for%20minority%20votes%26quot%3B.%20Alleging%20that%20it%20was%20a%20communal%20statement%2C%20the%20Congress%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20where%20Mr%20Sarma%20was%20speaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20Assam's%20Legislative%20assembly%20on%20the%20Opposition's%20adjournment%20motion%20on%20several%20key%20issues%20--%20including%20rape%20of%20minors%20and%20the%20targetting%20of%20Bengali%20Muslims%20in%20upper%20Assam's%20Sivasagar%20district%20--%20Mr%20Sarma%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20take%20sides.%20What%20can%20you%20do%3F%20Will%20not%20let%20Miya%20Muslims%20take%20over%20Assam%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20them%20(the%20Opposition)%20compete%20for%20minority%20votes.%20I%20am%20not%20in%20the%20competition%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20'Miya'%20refers%20to%20Muslims%20of%20Bengali%20origin%2C%20who%20are%20often%20accused%20of%20being%20illegal%20immigrants%20from%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%20said%20Opposition%20leaders%20Rafikul%20Sahab%20and%20Debabrata%20Saikia%20have%20made%20an%20important%20statement.%20The%20two%20leaders%20had%20underscored%20that%20people%20will%20move%20from%20Lower%20Assam%20to%20upper%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestioning%20why%20that%20would%20happen%2C%20Mr%20Sarma%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20Miya%20Muslims%20will%20take%20the%20entire%20lower%20Assam%3F%20We%20will%20not%20let%20you%20all%20to%20take%20the%20lower%20Assam%2C%20no%20never%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma's%20remarks%20come%20two%20days%20after%20Opposition%20MLA%20Akhil%20Gogoi%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20recreate%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20episodes%20in%20Assam.%20His%20comments%20followed%20reports%20that%20some%20organisations%20have%20allegedly%20been%20threatening%20Muslims%20from%20Upper%20Assam%2C%20demanding%20that%20they%20leave%20the%20administrative%20division.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20All-India%20United%20Democratic%20Front%20(AIUDF)%20has%20written%20to%20Governor%20Lakshman%20Prasad%20Acharya%2C%20seeking%20action%20against%20unknown%20organisations%20and%20fundamentalist%20groups%20issuing%20threats%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community%20in%20Upper%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20reporters%20later%2C%20Opposition%20leader%20Debabrata%20Saikia%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20so%20many%20instances%20of%20failure%20of%20law%20and%20order%20--%20rape%2C%20dacoity%2C%20murder%20etc.%20We%20have%20given%20statistics%20about%20it.%20There%20have%20been%20more%20than%2020%20cases%20of%20murder%20and%20arson%20in%20just%20seven%20days%20in%20June%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20BJP%20rule%20started%2C%20there%20have%20been%20at%20least%20six%20cases%20of%20rape%20per%20day%20--%20which%20is%20more%20than%20the%20last%2015%20years%20Congress%20rule%20in%20Assam%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20trying%20to%20say%20that%20a%20particular%20community%20was%20involved.%20There%20was%20assault%20on%20Indian%20citizens%20belonging%20to%20the%20minority%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Saikia%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20statistics%20don't%20say%20such%20thing.%20So%20we%20have%20asked%20for%20a%20discussion%20regarding%20the%20matter.%20But%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20saying%20very%20communal%20thing.%20We%20have%20protested%20and%20walk%20out%20from%20the%20assembly%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Saikia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724758620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F9rijhs18_himanta-sarma_625x300_18_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-allow-muslims-to-take-over-state-assam-chief-minister