0statements%20featured%20heavily%20in%20bail%20pleas%20filed%20by%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20and%20Mr%20Sisodia%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Mr%20Sisodia%20was%20granted%20bail%20by%20the%20top%20court%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20had%20noted%20that%20he%20had%20spent%20nearly%2018%20months%20in%20jail%20and%20there%20was%20no%20prospect%20of%20a%20trial%20anytime%20soon.%20To%20keep%20him%20in%20prison%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Btravesty%20of%20justice%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanish-sisodia-has-right-to-speedy-trial-says-supreme-court-6297896%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BTravesty%20Of%20Justice%26quot%3B%3A%20Sisodia%20Gets%20Bail%2C%20Top%20Court%20Slams%20Delay%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20has%20also%20contested%20charges%20against%20him%20by%20noting%20the%20material%20is%20based%20on%20approvers'%20statements%2C%20remains%20in%20jail.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-interim-bail-for-delhi-chief-minister-arvind-kejriwal-by-supreme-court-6334040%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20given%20bail%20in%20the%20ED%20case%20but%20not%20yet%20in%20the%20CBI%20case%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFormatting%20Phone%20Not%20%26quot%3BCriminal%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20on%2C%20the%20court%20also%20dismissed%20the%20prosecution's%20claim%20that%20Ms%20Kavitha%20had%20deleted%20incriminating%20content%20from%20mobile%20phones%20by%20formatting%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPhones%20are%20a%20private%20thing...%20people%20delete%20messages%20(all%20the%20time).%20I%20have%20a%20habit%20of%20deleting%20group%20messages...%20these%20school%20and%20college%20groups%20post%20many%20messages.%20(This%20is)%20normal%20human%20conduct...%20anyone%20in%20this%20room%20wi