%20of%20being%20controlled%20by%20them%2C''%20the%20document%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20curriculum%20advises%20adolescents%20to%20suppress%20their%20natural%20sexual%20impulses%20by%20avoiding%20media%20and%20publications%20that%20might%20arouse%20them.%20It%20also%20suggests%20that%20exercise%20and%20other%20distractions%20can%20help%20divert%20attention%20away%20from%20%26quot%3Bundesirable%20activities%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20curriculum%20covers%20four%20key%20topics%20to%20educate%20students%20on%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERelationship%20between%20love%20and%20sex%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEstablishing%20and%20maintaining%20healthy%20boundaries%20in%20intimate%20relationships%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWays%20to%20cope%20with%20sexual%20fantasies%20and%20impulses%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EConsequences%20of%20poor%20handling%20of%20intimate%20relationships%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Lovers%20who%20are%20unable%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20consequences%20of%20premarital%20sex%2C%20such%20as%20unwed%20marital%20pregnancy%2C%20legal%20consequences%20and%20emotional%20distress%2C%20should%20firmly%20refuse%20to%20have%20sex%20before%20marriage%2C''%20the%20material%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teaching%20material%20offers%20creative%20solutions%20for%20pupils%20to%20manage%20sexual%20impulses%2C%20including%20avoidance%20and%20diversion%20techniques.%C2%A0The%20guidelines%20further%20dictate%20what%20students%20should%20wear%2C%20cautioning%20against%20%26quot%3Bsexy%20clothing%26quot%3B%20that%20might%20cause%20%26quot%3Bvisual%20stimulation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20outdated%20and%20repressive%20approach%20has%20been%20widely%20criticised%20for%20shaming%20and%20stigmatising%20healthy%20sexual%20development%2C%20rather%20than%20providing%20comprehensive%20and%20inclusive%20sex%20education.%20Diana%20Kwok%2C%20professor%20of%20gender%20studies%20at%20the%20Education%20University%20of%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2C%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Feducation%2Farticle%2F3275787%2Fbadminton-hong-kong-answer-sexual-impulses-schoolchildren-we-ask-experts%5C%22%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20the%20authorities%20should%20not%20emphasise%20the%20need%20to%20control%20sexual%20development%2C%20but%20instead%20teach%20young%20people%20how%20to%20face%20or%20understand%20it.%20Another%20critic%20called%20the%20suggestions%20''out%20of%20touch''%20and%20unrealistic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20internet%20also%20couldn't%20resist%20poking%20fun%20at%20these%20suggestions%2C%20joking%20that%20%26quot%3Bbadminton%26quot%3B%20might%20become%20Hong%20Kong's%20version%20of%20%26quot%3BNetflix%20and%20chill%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Education%20Bureau%20insisted%20that%20its%20controversial%20guidelines%20are%20intended%20to%20empower%20students%20to%20make%20%26quot%3Bresponsible%20decisions%26quot%3B%20about%20their%20relationships%20and%20sexuality.%20The%20Bureau%20maintained%20that%20its%20suggestions%20are%20necessary%20to%20help%20young%20people%20navigate%20the%20complexities%20of%20adolescence%20and%20make%20informed%20choices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724756700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fcvinsg2g_badminton_625x300_27_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbadminton-and-books-hong-kongs-bizarre-fix-for-teens-to-fight-sexual-temptation-6428628%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20teaching%20material%20offers%20creative%20solutions%20for%20pupils%20to%20manage%20sexual%20impulses%2C%20including%20avoidance%20and%20diversion%20techniques.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbadminton-and-books-hong-kongs-bizarre-fix-for-teens-to-fight-sexual-temptation-6428628%22%2C%22