send%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F227895%2Findia-best-bakeries-iconic-kayani-pune-kolkata-nahoum-glenary-wengers-delhi-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edough%20and%20cakes%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20when%20they%20needed%20to%20be%20baked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Kyani%20%26amp%3B%20Co%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZoroastrian%20migration%20and%20its%20attendant%20cuisine%20have%20been%20grafting%20itself%20into%20Indian%20gastronomy%20since%20the%2010th%20century%20when%20Iranian%20immigrants%20began%20flocking%20to%20the%20city.%20They%20left%20an%20indelible%20mark%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20culinary%20canvas.%20One%20of%20these%20legacy%20eateries%20where%20this%20is%20visible%20is%20the%20Kyani%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20This%20Parsi%20cafe%20was%20born%20in%201904%20when%20a%20gentleman%20Khodram%20Marezaban%20willed%20to%20bring%20the%20unique%20%3Cem%3EIrani%3C%2Fem%3E%20cuisine%20taste%20to%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fbreakfast-in-mumbai-1-1723630692.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kyani%20%26amp%3B%20Co%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20iconic%20Parsi%20bakeries%20in%20Mumbai%20that%20serves%20authentic%20Parsi%20fare%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fbreakfast-in-mumbai-1-1723630692.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fbreakfast-in-mumbai-1-1723630692-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fbreakfast-in-mumbai-1-1723630692-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fbreakfast-in-mumbai-1-1723630692-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fbreakfast-in-mumbai-1-1723630692-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361315%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKyani%20%26amp%3B%20Co%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20iconic%20Parsi%20bakeries%20in%20Mumbai%20that%20serves%20authentic%20Parsi%20fare%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20LHS%3A%20Instagram%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fanecdotes_by_ruchee%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERuchi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20RHS%3A%20Instagram%3A%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Flets_comfort_it%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Food%20and%20Comfort%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20red%20checkered%20mats%20on%20the%20tables%20are%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20colonial%20setting%20in%20which%20the%20Parsi%20cafe%20scaled.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F321953%2Flist-of-eight-iconic-irani-cafes-in-mumbai-britannia-kyani-yazdani-ideal-corner%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKyani%20%26amp%3B%20Co%20is%20a%20favourite%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20almost%20everyone%20who%20has%20walked%20through%20its%20rustic%20doors%2C%20and%20food%20writer%20Kalyan%20Karmarkar%20is%20no%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20wriote%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3Ekheema%20%3C%2Fem%3Eat%20Kyani%20was%20indeed%20good.%20The%20meat%20and%20spices%20were%20robust%2C%20not%20smelly%20or%20too%20oily%20as%20it%20is%20in%20many%20of%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20iconic%20%3Cem%3Ekheema%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplaces.%20The%20%3Cem%3Eporo%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Cem%3EParsi%3C%2Fem%3E-style%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20%3C%2Fem%3Eomelette)%20was%20pretty%20much%20the%20way%20my%20mom-in-law%20makes%20it%20and%20way%20tastier%20in%20this%20