%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Transfer%20the%20plants%20to%20larger%20pots%20after%20around%2010%20days.%20Opt%20for%20a%2012%20to%2018%20inch%20pot%20with%20a%20good%20drainage%20system%20for%20the%20mature%20custard%20apple%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20For%20the%20potting%20mix%2C%20use%2020%20percent%20sand%2Fcocopeat%2C%2030%20percent%20vermicompost%2C%20and%20garden%20soil.%20Add%20neem%20cake%20on%20top%20of%20the%20mixture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20Initially%2C%20place%20the%20plant%20in%20a%20semi-shaded%20area%20for%20a%20few%20days%20and%20gradually%20shift%20it%20to%20a%20sunny%20location.%20Ensure%20the%20custard%20apple%20tree%20receives%20six%20to%20eight%20hours%20of%20sunlight%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7.%20Water%20the%20plant%20regularly%20and%20maintain%20proper%20care%20throughout%20its%20growth%20stages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8.%20Expect%20the%20custard%20apple%20tree%20to%20bear%20fruits%20within%20two%20to%20three%20years%2C%20with%20optimal%20fruiting%20after%20three%20to%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9.%20Maintain%20a%20nutrient-rich%20soil%20mix%20and%20supplement%20the%20plant%20with%20cow%20dung%20manure%2C%20neem%20cake%20powder%2C%20and%20banana%20peel%20powder%20mixture%20regularly.%20Use%20biozyme%20granules%20for%20added%20nutrition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10.%20Occasionally%20weed%20the%20soil%20to%20keep%20it%20aerated.%20Prune%20the%20plant%20after%20two%20years%20to%20control%20its%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20why%20wait%3F%20With%20these%20simple%20steps%2C%20start%20your%20custard%20apple%20gardening%20journey%20today%20and%20relish%20the%20bountiful%20rewards%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F302682%2Fcustard-apple-sitaphal-health-benefits-winter-fruit-immunity-boosting-fights-anaemia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20nutritious%20produce%3C%2Fa%3E%20right%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHappy%20gardening!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%