%3Cp%3ETeachers%20are%20encouraged%20to%20teach%20this%20way%2C%20without%20poring%20over%20the%20books.%20Seeing%20the%20success%20of%20the%20school%2C%20the%20village%20%3Cem%3Emukhiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(head)%20gave%20them%20the%20community%20centre%2C%20where%20classes%20are%20conducted%20during%20the%20rainy%20season.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20ahead%2C%20Angshuman%20hopes%20to%20purchase%20some%20land%20and%20set%20up%20a%20school%20with%20an%20eco-friendly%20campus.%20He%20also%20wishes%20to%20set%20up%20a%20computer%20lab%20and%20library%20for%20the%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThrough%20this%20initiative%20and%20the%20children%2C%20we%20hope%20to%20improve%20the%20economy%20of%20the%20village.%20We%20are%20sowing%20the%20seeds%20of%20entrepreneurship%20in%20these%20children%2C%20which%20will%20reach%20the%20community%20and%20improve%20their%20livelihoods%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Angshuman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296463%2Fjharkhand-teacher-sapan-patralekh-teaches-parents-and-grandparents-improves-literacy-rate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eschool%20currently%20has%20105%20students%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20kindergarten%20to%20Class%2012%20and%20seven%20teachers.%20It%20costs%20Rs%20300%20per%20child%20per%20month%2C%20which%20is%20Rs%203%2C600%20per%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20support%20a%20child%20by%20donating%20through%20UPI%20on%207001714095%40axl%20or%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccount%20no%3A%2041165791703%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EName%3A%20Gach%20Green%20Hands%20Social%20Welfare%20Trust%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIFSC%3A%20SBIN0018784%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Angshuman%20Thakur%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724075548000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgacher-skul-min-1724074337.jpg%22%2C%22origin